reviewText: My 1 year old loves Elmo and this movie had her giggling and dancing the whole way thru. Did not dissapoint
This helps my daughter not be so scared of things like the dark
Bought for Great Grandson, he is not afraid of anything, and does not even cry if he gets hurt.  Being brave will help him more I think.
I purchased Sesame Street: Being Brave for my granddaghter and she watches it over & over again.  I hope to continue purchasing this genre of film in the future.
